    "bio": "Automation Architect | I transform complexity into simplicity\nBuilding intelligent n8n workflows that do your heavy lifting in minutes, not hours. My mission: Eliminate repetitive tasks, streamline your operations, and give you back the most valuable resource – your time. Let’s make work feel lighter together.",
    "verified": true,
